5 USE CASES OF BLOCKCHAIN

1. Cryptocurrency & Digital Payments
Enables peer-to-peer digital money transfer
No banks or intermediaries required
Fast and low-cost international payments
Examples: Bitcoin, Ethereum

2. Supply Chain Management
Tracks products from origin to consumer
Improves transparency and traceability
Prevents fraud and duplication
Used in food, medicine, and logistics

3. Smart Contracts
Self-executing digital contracts
Automatically enforce rules and conditions
No third-party involvement
Used in insurance and real estate

4. Digital Identity
Secure identity verification
Reduces identity theft and fraud
User-controlled personal data
Used in e-governance and KYC

5. Healthcare Records
Secure storage of medical data
Easy data sharing among hospitals
Prevents data tampering
Improves patient privacy

ðŸ”‘ One-Line:
Blockchain is used in payments, supply chains, smart contracts, digital identity, and healthcare for secure and transparent data management.
